Shibin  
Phone: +91 9061393493 |E-mail: shibi393493@gmail.com  
LinkedIn: Shibin Shibi | GitHub: shibinshibii | See Portfolio  
  
  
 
FULL STACK DEVELOPER  
  
Passionate and results-driven Full Stack Developer specializing in Python and JavaScript. Experienced in 
building scalable, dynamic, and user-friendly web applications. Skilled in both frontend and backend 
technologies, with a strong foundation in Django, React, REST APIs, and database management. Adept 
at problem-solving and continuously learning new technologies to deliver innovative solutions.  
  
 
  
SKILLS  
  
Programming Languages: Python, JavaScript, HTML, CSS  
Frameworks & Libraries: Django, Django Rest Framework, React, Bootstrap  
Databases: MySQL, MongoDB, PostgreSQL 
Version Control & Tools: Git, GitHub, RESTful APIs, AJAX, Fetch API  
  
  
 
PROJECTS EXPERIENCE  
  
Django eCommerce website  
  
• Developed a fully functional e-commerce platform with features like product browsing, cart 
management, secure checkout, and order tracking.  
• Implemented real-time cart updates using AJAX & Fetch API to enhance user experience.  
• Integrated SQLite for database management and Django Authentication for user security.  
• Tech Stack: Django, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, AJAX.   
Random Quote Generator  
    
• Built a dynamic quote generator that fetches and displays random motivational quotes.  
• Integrated APIs to retrieve quotes dynamically, ensuring a seamless user experience.  
• Tech Stack: Django, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, API Integration.
